[head=3][color=#c0753b]Overview[/color][/head]  
Under Article 5.4 of the Intercorporate Transition and Rehabilitation Agreement, Waffles Co. authorizes the reassignment of [bold]Kairon Orsen Sera[/bold], previously Lead Security Operative under the Heat & Pressure Tactical Division, to Nanotrasen’s Security Cadet Program.  

The operative’s redeployment follows the conclusion of internal black-ops contract [italic]Project Black Cat[/italic], with classified operational records sealed and transferred under joint custody. This transition aims to stabilize subject performance, reintegrate field discipline, and maintain intercorporate stability following recent high-intensity missions.  

[color=#c0753b]──────────────────────────────────────[/color]

[head=3][color=#c0753b]Behavioral and Operational Evaluation[/color][/head]  
Waffles tactical analysis confirms exemplary leadership during active conflict. Subject exhibits advanced containment expertise and asset protection capability.  
Observed tendencies: sustained hypervigilance, mild aggression spikes under duress, adherence to hierarchy intact.  
Recommendation: continued duty under structured chain-of-command to ensure reconditioning.  

Authorization Chain:  
• Chief Tactical Officer [bold]Baker Whiskey[/bold]  
• Liaison Officer [bold]Lt. R. “Syrup” Valentine[/bold]  
